data.description: You will love the charm of this 1902 two story home on Main Street! You are welcomed into the home by a beautiful entry way with gorgeous stairway. There are 2 living spaces & a beautiful large dining room with a bench window seat. On the back of the home is the large kitchen with TONS of original cabinets for storage space along with a unique stove/oven. The side entry brings you into the laundry room w/ a half bath. All 3 of the spacious bedrooms on the 2nd floor have tall ceilings & ample closet space. There is a 3rd level finished BONUS room. From the back staircase to the hardwood doors, you love all of the character this home as to offer. Front screened in porch, fully fenced in back yard & 2 car detached garage complete this home.
